consumption without any loss of cleaning quality.Easy to service: HF industrial washing machines have easily accessible parts in order to keep maintenance and service as quick and cost-effective as possible.',NULL,'http://www.ipso.be/myImages/01/012/hf185-front_cygnusprof.gif',1,NULL,NULL),(10,1,'IPH : \'Hard mount\' high spin washer extractors from 17,8 to 79,3 kg','Long life reliability: At IPSO, we understand what you need from your commercial laundry equipment: industrial laundry is more demanding than home laundry, and needs robust equipment. Hard-wearing IPSO IPH washer extractors are perfect for commercial laundry: as with all our industrial products, our washer-extractors have been engineered to high standards - giving them the long life and reliability you have come to expect from us.User friendly, simple and safe: The user-friendly controls and the large door openings to easily load and unload are appreciated by all users. The IPH machines comply with the strictest industry safety regulations.Energy efficient: Ipso IPH washers offer you the most flexible programming options in order to ensure you the lowest energy consumptions whilst maintaining optimal wash results.Easy to service: The major components of the IPH machines are all easily accessible and maintenance and service is fast and economical.',NULL,'http://www.ipso.be/myImages/01/001/001/iph175_2.jpg',1,NULL,NULL),(11,1,'WF: \'Hard mount\' normal spin washer extractors from 6,5 to 40 kg','Long life & reliability: IPSO WF washer-extractors have been developed to provide the long life and reliability that industries demand from a washing machine. For our full range of washer-extractors, scroll down the menu on the left-hand side of this page.User-friendly, simple and safe: The controls on the WF line are incredibly easy to understand, ensuring professional washing quality with every wash. The industrial washing machines\' large doors make loading and unloading simple, making the appliances even easier to use. WF industrial washing machines all comply with the strictest industry safety regulations.Energy efficient: IPSO WF washers offer you flexible energy programming options, so you can get fantastic results from our industrial washing machines while using minimal power.Easy to service: The major components of the WF industrial washing machine are all easily accessible, allowing easy and efficient maintenance and service.',NULL,'http://www.ipso.be/myImages/01/001/001/wf.jpg',1,NULL,NULL),(12,1,'HM : Barrier washer extractors from 16 to 90 kg','Hospital & health care environments are nowadays faced with an increasing threat of microbiological contaminations, the so called ‘hospital acquired infections’ (HAI). These environments all count numerous places where the risk of transmitting microbiological contamination is high. The interrelation of these places simplifies the spread of bacteria.This risk also affects the laundry process. Bacteria coming from soiled linen through air, hands or human contact during improper handling or processing of laundry are an important cause of infection. Therefore, hospital & health care environments need to take preventive measures in order to avoid microbiological contamination in the laundry process. The HM-range of barrier washer extractors offers a solution for this threat as it considerably reduces the risk of recontamination or cross contamination thanks to its ‘dual door’ design. The barrier washer extractors are built ‘in’ a physical wall separating the loading & unloading side. This set-up ensures an optimal sanitation and avoids contact between clean, disinfected laundry & soiled, contaminated linen.  What are hospital-acquired infections?Hospital acquired infections (HAI) or ’nosocomial’ infections affect patients during their stay in hospital. One of the most recurrent pathogens that occur with these infections is MRSA or methicillin resistant Staphylococcus aureus. The term MRSA is used to describe organisms that are resistant to commonly used antibiotics. Currently MRSA contaminations are on the rise in hospital & health care institutions, resulting in a greater risk of mortality and significantly higher treatment costs for patients with surgical side infections. Taking measures in the laundry process to reduce the risk of MRSA is therefore an absolute necessity.',NULL,'http://www.ipso.be/myImages/01/001/001/groep-1-kopie.gif',1,NULL,NULL),(13,1,'CWDS : Laundry equipment for semi-commercial use','Long life reliability: The Ipso CWDS range has been developed with a focus on the legendary Ipso long life reliability we have been known for since our existence.User friendly, simple and safe: Our user friendly controls on the CWDS line are a dream for every professional. The large door openings to easily load and unload are appreciated by all users. The CWDS machines comply with the strictest industry safety regulations.Energy efficient: The Ipso CWDS range offers you the most flexible programming options in order to ensure you the lowest energy consumptions whilst maintaining optimal wash results.Easy to service: The major components of the CWDS machines are all easily accessible and maintenance and service is fast and economical.',NULL,'http://www.ipso.be/myImages/01/001/005/cwds-8-centurion-0001.gif',1,NULL,NULL),(14,1,'Cygnus Modular Controls','IPSO sets a new standard in the field of washer extractor controls with ‘Cygnus Modular Controls’, a state-of-the-art range of controls, cost-saving & unlimited in flexibility. The combination of IPSO laundry equipment with Cygnus controls will guarantee an outstanding wash result. Thanks to its long lasting experience in the laundry business, IPSO has been able to create \'Cygnus Modular Controls’, a complete & innovative range of microprocessor controls entirely developed in-house.‘Modular’ is the key word of Cygnus: the same main module, used for the complete range of washer extractors, is extendable according to the needs of the individual user.‘Cygnus Modular Controls’ are available in 4 standard versions (Standard, Commercial, Premium and Professional) which each have a number of well-determined features and benefits. The most basic control (Cygnus Standard) has a number of standard wash programmes and limited functions, while the most comprehensive control (Cygnus Professional) allows modification of every parameter, even during the wash cycle.The Cygnus software tool allowing creation and/or modification of wash programmes on PC/laptop is the Cygnus Assist. This software has been developed to run in a user-friendly Windows-environment.',NULL,'http://www.ipso.be/myImages/01/012/cmc.gif',1,NULL,NULL),(15,1,'CD : Energy efficient tumble dryers from 6,5 to 28 kg','Long life & reliability: IPSO CD commercial dryers are designed to be reliable and durable, ensuring a longer life and reduced maintenance costs.User-friendly, simple and safe: The user-friendly controls on the CD appliances make operation of our commercial dryers quick and easy. The loading and unloading of laundry is also made easy by the larger than normal doors. CD commercial tumble dryers comply with all industry safety regulations.Energy efficient: IPSO CD commercial dryers offer you a wide choice of programming options, enabling you to choose the most economical and power-saving drying service.Easy to service: The major components of the CD commercial dryers are easily accessed making maintenance quick and easy.',NULL,'http://www.ipso.be/myImages/01/001/002/cd220_2.jpg',1,NULL,NULL),(16,1,'DR : Industrial tumble dryers from 8,5 to 56 kg','Long-life & reliability: As with all our industrial products, IPSO DR industrial dryers have been engineered to high standards - giving them the long life and reliability you have come to expect from us.User friendly, simple and safe: The user-friendly controls on the DR range of industrial dryers make large-scale drying easy! The large door openings to easily load and unload and are appreciated by all users. DR industrial dryers comply with the strictest industry safety regulations.Energy efficient: IPSO DR dryers offer you the most flexible programming options to ensure your energy consumption remains low - while giving you great drying results. As with all IPSO industrial products, energy efficiency and impressive performance go hand in hand.Easy to service: The major components of the DR industrial dryers are all easily accessible, making maintaining and servicing our industrial drying equipment fast and economical.',NULL,'http://www.ipso.be/myImages/01/001/002/001/droger_group.gif',1,NULL,NULL),(17,1,'Control options for tumble dryers','Flexibility: The IPSO-controls allow the user to adapt several parameters to his needs, ensuring a drying result that meets his standards.User friendly: The IPSO-controls are incredibly easy to understand, ensuring professional washing quality with every drying cycle.',NULL,'http://www.ipso.be/myImages/01/001/006/controls-dryers.jpg',1,NULL,NULL),(18,4,'RI : Roller ironers with 250mm & 300mm roller diameter','Long life reliability: Ipso RI roller ironers have been developed with a focus on the legendary Ipso long life reliability we have been known for since our existence.User friendly, simple and safe: Our user friendly controls on the RI line are a dream for every professional. The robust wooden feeding plate for the RI ironers is appreciated by all users. The RI ironers comply with the strictest industry safety regulations.Energy efficient: Ipso RI roller ironers offer you the most flexible programming options in order to ensure you the lowest energy consumptions whilst maintaining top ironing quality.Easy to service: The major components of the RI ironers are all easily accessible and maintenance and service is fast and economical.',NULL,'http://www.ipso.be/myImages/01/001/003/iri-01_ipso_1.gif',1,NULL,NULL),(19,4,'CI : Flatwork ironers with 325mm & 500mm roller diameter','Long life reliability: Ipso CI flatwork ir